room_title: Escape room "Carnival of Mystery" by Escape SBC in Shreveport
room_description: Ah…the old carnival grounds.  It was such fun to play all the games when you were younger, but now they are all closed up.  “Let’s just sneak in and play a few of the games.”  Oops…the gate locked behind you!  Can you play all of the games to find the key to the exit gate before the old carnies come back and make you their next side-show attraction??
